ying-tips-cost-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20I%20chose%20to%20lease%20because%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20figured%20the%20EV%20landscape%20would%20change%20a%20lot%20over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20lease%2C%20and%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20that%20was%20the%20best%20financial%20decision.%20I%20ended%20up%20buying%20out%20the%20lease%2C%20too.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Bolt%20is%20the%20slowest%20of%20fast-charging%20cars%2C%20and%20that's%20the%20biggest%20downside%20to%20it.%20What%20I%20didn't%20expect%20is%20a%20kind%20of%20pooh-poohing%20at%20Bolt%20drivers%20specifically%2C%20because%20our%20cars%20charge%20slowly.%20Other%20EV%20drivers%20get%20upset%20at%20us%20taking%20up%20time%20at%20charging%20stations.%20The%20next%20EV%20for%20us%20will%20be%20something%20that%20can%20charge%20faster.%20We've%20got%20our%20eye%20on%20the%20Equinox.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20only%20have%20Level-1%20charging%20at%20home%2C%20because%20we%20just%20don't%20need%20anything%20else.%20My%20husband%20has%20free%20Level-2%20charging%20at%20work%2C%20and%20I%20also%20had%20that%20for%20some%20time.%20We%20public%20charge%20when%20we%20road%20trip%2C%20so%20that's%20the%20most%20we%20ever%20pay.%20Just%20something%20I've%20become%20used%20to%20is%3A%20Always%20have%20a%20backup%20plan.%20Make%20sure%20you%20understand%20how%20fast%20charging%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBob%20McGill%2C%2078%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0League%20City%2C%20TX%20%E2%80%94%20Tesla%20Model%203%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20stands%20in%20front%20of%20his%20Tesla%20in%20a%20driveway.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653fe0a296f7540cd06965b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBob%20McGill%20drives%20a%20Tesla.%3Cp%3EBob%20McGill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20August%202022%2C%20I%20took%20delivery%20of%20a%20new%20Tesla%20Model%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20been%20thinking%20about%20it%20for%20a%20while%20for%20all%20the%20usual%20things%2C%20like%20not%20having%20to%20buy%20gas%2C%20and%20I'm%20a%20retired%20computer%20nerd%20so%20I%20like%20cutting-edge%20technology.%20I%20considered%20the%20Nissan%20Leaf%20for%20a%20while%20and%20the%20Chevrolet%20Bolt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20primarily%20charge%20at%20home%20and%20rarely%20charge%20outside%20the%20house.%20I%20bought%20the%20home%20charging%20unit%20from%20Tesla%2C%20and%20an%20electrician%20friend%20installed%20it%20for%20me.%20It%20costs%20about%20%2450%20per%20month%20for%20electricity.%20I%20don't%20plug%20it%20in%20every%20night.%20I%20get%20about%20300%20miles%20on%20a%20charge%20and%20I%20have%20over%2022%2C000%20miles%20on%20the%20car%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou're%20not%20having%20to%20do%20any%20maintenance.%20There's%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20learning%20curve%20about%20charging.%20There%20was%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20anxiety%20at%20first%20about%20being%20able%20to%20charge%20whenever%20I%20needed%20to.%20But%20it%20turns%20out%2C%20there's%20plenty%20around.%20It's%20not%20difficult%20to%20do%20that.%20I%20took%20a%20trip%20to%20Alabama%20in%20May%2C%20and%20I've%20never%20driven%20the%20Tesla%20over%20there%2C%20but%20I%20was%20able%20to%20find%20places%20to%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20somebody%20feels%20like%20EV%20is%20what%20they%20want%20to%20do%2C%20they%20should.%20They're%20a%20little%20more%20expensive%2C%20but%20the%20amount%20of%20gas%20savings%20will%20make%20up%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELisa%20Holland%2C%2059%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0Atlanta%2C%20GA%20%E2%80%94%20Ford%20Mustang%20Mach-E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222663%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20stands%20in%20front%20of%20her%20silver%20SUV%20in%20front%20of%20a%20lake%20with%20green%20trees.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653fdf8e0487ff031cb2263b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223551%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELisa%20Holland%20own