%20political%20manoeuvring%2C%20it%20is%20incumbent%20upon%20the%20Congress%20to%20sincerely%20apologise%20for%20their%20involvement%20in%20the%20unrest.%20In%20his%20emerging%20role%20as%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20leader%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20with%20his%20pledge%20to%20foster%20love%20in%20a%20realm%20rife%20with%20hatred%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3ENafrat%20ke%20bazaar%20me%20mohhabbat%20ki%20dukaan%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0should%20take%20the%20lead%20in%20initiating%20the%20process%20of%20reconciliation%20and%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%201984%20Sikh%20massacre%20not%20only%20resulted%20in%20the%20loss%20of%20life%20but%20also%20dealt%20a%20devastating%20blow%20to%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20dignity%20and%20pride.%20Echoing%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20Nanavati%20Commission%20report%2C%20the%20riots%20not%20only%20inflicted%20pain%20on%20the%20Sikh%20populace%20but%20also%20jolted%20the%20conscience%20of%20all%20right-thinking%20individuals%20across%20the%20nation.%20The%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20investigations%20into%20the%20cases%20in%20Delhi%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20such%20as%20Bokaro%20and%20Kanpur%2C%20unearthed%20not%20just%20mass%20killings%20but%20also%20the%20active%20participation%20of%20Congress%20workers%20and%20certain%20%E2%80%98prominent%E2%80%99%20leaders%20of%20this%20party.%20Despite%20affording%20these%20leaders%20the%20opportunity%20to%20defend%20themselves%2C%20they%20failed%20to%20provide%20a%20compelling%20defence%20and%20instead%20resorted%20to%20manipulating%20facts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENearly%20four%20decades%20have%20passed%20since%20those%20tragic%20events%20unfolded.%20While%20some%20advocate%20for%20the%20Sikh%20community%20to%20move%20on%20and%20introspect%2C%20it%20is%20unjust%20to%20sweep%20their%20anguish%20and%20trauma%20under%20the%20rug.%20Numerous%20reports%2C%20including%20those%20by%20the%20Nanavati%20Commission%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdelhi-hc-1984-massacres-a-crime-against-humanity-india-must-plug-legal-loopholes%5C%22%3E2018%20verdict%20by%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20indicate%20that%20Sikhs%20have%20been%20hesitant%20to%20share%20their%20narratives%20with%20the%20world%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20sense%20of%20isolation%20and%20alienation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20adage%20%E2%80%9Cjustice%20delayed%20is%20justice%20denied%E2%80%9D%20rings%20true.%20The%20Sikh%20community%20has%20been%20losing%20faith%20in%20the%20judicial%20system%2C%20and%20this%20feeling%20of%20alienation%20is%20deeply%20ingrained%20in%20their%20lived%20experiences.%20While%20Justice%20S.%20Muralidhar%20displayed%20sensitivity%20and%20humility%20in%20acknowledging%20the%20pain%2C%20suffering%20and%20trauma%20endured%20by%20the%20Sikh%20community%2C%20his%20sentencing%20of%20culprits%20such%20as%20Sajjan%20Kumar%20and%20various%20Congress%20workers%20begs%20the%20larger%20question%20%E2%80%93%20can%20it%20truly%20be%20considered%20justice%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Review%3A%20India%20in%201984%2C%20and%20a%20World%20Bound%20By%20Compassion%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fradhika-oberoi-stillborn-season%5C%22%3EIndia%20in%201984%2C%20and%20a%20World%20Bound%20By%20Compassion%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20primary%20issues%20at%20hand%20is%20the%20refusal%20of%20the%20perpetrators%20to%20accept%20responsibility%20for%20their%20actions.%20Leaders%20such%20as%20Kamal%20Nath%20and%20Jagdish%20Tytler%20are%20yet%20to%20apologise%20or%20even%20admit%20their%20involvement%2C%20despite%20eyewitness%20accounts%20presented%20in%20court.%20Disturbingly%2C%20not%20only%20have%20these%20culprits%E2%80%99%20evaded%20justice%2C%20but%20they%20have%20also%20been%20rewarded%20with%20high%20political%20positions%2C%20including%20roles%20as%20MLAs%2C%20MPs%2C%20ministers%20and%20even%20chief%20minister.%20Even%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZb01XTXPfLg%5C%22%3Eadmitted%20in%20a%20television%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20certain%20Congress%20leaders%20were%20complicit%20in%20the%20tragic%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20Nanavati%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20to%20the%20conscience%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20the%20liberal%20section%20of%20Indian%20society%20has%20failed%20to%20recognise%20the%20Sikh%20community%20as%20victims.%20The%20term%20%E2%80%98riots%E2%80%99%20itself%20is%20a%20bone%20of%20contention%20for%20Sikhs%2C%20as%20it%20implies%20clashes%20between%20two%20sides%2C%20whereas%20the%20events%20of%201984%20constituted%20targeted%20violence%2C%20akin%20to%20genocide%2C%20with%20Sikhs%20as%20the%20sole%20victims.%20While%20the%20liberal%20section%20raises%20concerns%20over%20the%20rehabilitation%20of%20rapists%20and%20the%20welcoming%20of%20accused%20individuals%2C%20they%20often%20fail%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20Congress%20leaders%20who%20have%20either%20been%20convicted%20or%20faced%20serious%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20queries%20about%20the%201984%20tragedy%20has%20been%20problematic.%20During%20his%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%2C%20he%20evaded%20condemning%20the%20events%20directly%2C%20instead%20referencing%20statements%20made%20by%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20and%20former%20Congress%20president%20Sonia%20Gandhi.%20His%20reluctance%20to%20apologise%20is%20disheartening%2C%20given%20his%20vocal%20pride%20in%20the%20achievements%20of%20his%20family%20members%2C%20such%20as%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20Rajiv%20Gandhi.%20If%20one%20takes%20pride%20in%20their%20virtues%2C%20one%20must%20acknowledge%20their%20vices%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20recent%20visit%20to%20Darbar%20Sahib%2C%20Amritsar%2C%20and%20his%20acts%20of%20%3Cem%3ESewa%3C%2Fem%3E%20during%20ordinary%20days%20of%20the%20Nanakshahi%20calendar%20may%20have%20been%20interpreted%20as%20a%20significant%20gesture%2C%20it%20remains%20imperative%20to%20question%20the%20concrete%20actions%20taken%20by%20the%20Congress%20and%20Gandhi%20towards%20reconciliation%20and%20the%20wellbeing%20of%20the%20families%20affected%20by%20the%201984%20tragedy.%20Nowadays%20Gandhi%20has%20been%20visiting%20various%20sections%20of%20society%20and%20sharing%20videos%20of%20his%20visits%20on%20social%20media.%20Can%20he%20pay%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20widow%20colony%20of%20Tilak%20Nagar%20in%20Delhi%2C%20where%20many%20men%20fell%20victim%20to%20the%20horrific%20events%20of%20November%201984%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22If%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20Asked%20About%20the%201984%20Killings%20Again%2C%20This%20is%20What%20He%20Should%20Say%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frahul-gandhi-congress-party-1984-riots%5C%22%3EIf%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20Asked%20About%20the%201984%20Killings%20Again%2C%20This%20is%20What%20He%20Should%20Say%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Frahul-gandhi-caste-census-obc-women-reservation-8951130%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHe%2520said%253A%2520%25E2%2580%259C100%2520per%2520cent%2Cthat%2520did%2520the%2520caste%2520census.%5C%22%3Erecent%20expression%20of%20regret%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20failure%20to%20conduct%20a%20caste%20census%20and%20implement%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservations%20is%20commendable.%20Shouldn%E2%80%99t%20the%20same%20regret%20be%20extended%20to%20the%20Sikh%20community%3F%20While%20these%20families%20require%20special%20social%20security%20measures%20and%20an%20environment%20conducive%20to%20their%20well-being%2C%20what%20Sikhs%20truly%20seek%20is%20a%20straightforward%20admission%20and%20apology%20from%20Gandhi%2C%20should%20he%20wish%20to%20be%20their%20leader.%20This%20sentiment%20resonates%20across%20the%20global%20Punjabi%20community.%20Rehabilitation%2C%20psychological%20support%20and%20community%20engagement%20can%20follow%2C%20but%20the%20initial%20acknowledgment%20of%20wrongdoing%20is%20a%20necessary%20step%20toward%20reconciliation%20and%20the%20restoration%20of%20respect%20for%20the%20Sikh%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20how%20many%20visits%20Gandhi%20makes%20to%20the%20gurudwaras%2C%20his%20trust%20among%20Sikhs%20and%20Punjabis%20will%20remain%20elusive%20unless%20he%20acknowledges%20past%20grievances%20and%20initiates%20dialogue%20for%20reconciliation.%20If%20he%20truly%20espouses%20the%20ethos%20of%20Sikhi%2C%20he%20must%20embody%20the%20principle%20of%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Mann%20niwan%2C%20matt%20uchi%20(%3C%2Fem%3Ebeing%20humble%20in%20mind%20and%20elevated%20in%20thinking)%E2%80%99%20and%20earnestly%20extend%20his%20goodwill%20towards%20the%20Sikh%20community.%20Electoral%20manoeuvring%20notwithstanding%2C%20the%20pressing%20reality%20is%20that%20Sikhs%20require%20a%20compassionate%20leader%20who%20is%20willing%20to%20lend%20an%20ear%2C%20facilitate%20healing%20and%20foster%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHarinder%20Happy%20is%20a%20PhD%20Scholar%20at%20the%20Centre%20of%20Social%20Medicine%20and%20Community%20Health%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20He%20can%20be%20reached%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharinderhappy.jnu%40gmail.com%5C%22%3Eharinderhappy.jnu%40gmail.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698827451000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01134213%2F3828685307_6cdc23ac11_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fcongress-must-apologise-for-the-1984-sikh-pogrom-will-rahul-gandhi-leading-the-charge%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rehabilitation%2C%20psychological%20support%20and%20community%20engagement%20can%20follow%2C%20but%20the%20initial%20acknowledgment%20of%20wrongdoing%20is%20a%20necessary%20step%20toward%20reconciliation%20and%20t