20%5Bhe%20and%20his%20brother%5D%20want%20to%20have%20dinner%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20is%20what%20he%20said%20when%20his%20life%20took%20a%20different%20turn%2C%20towards%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGaza%20has%20become%20a%20graveyard%20of%20children%2C%20UN%20Children%E2%80%99s%20Fund%20(UNICEF)%20spokesman%20James%20Elder%20stated%20during%20a%20news%20briefing%20in%20Geneva%20on%20October%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20an%20unspeakable%20situation%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EOn%20October%2031%2C%20the%20Gaza%20health%20ministry%20issued%20a%20statement%20that%20of%20the%208%2C525%20Palestinians%20killed%20in%20the%20past%20three%20weeks%2C%202%2C187%20were%20women%20and%203%2C542%20were%20children.%20That%20means%2041%25%20of%20those%20killed%20so%20far%20have%20been%20children.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EOver%206%2C000%20children%20have%20been%20injured%20and%20about%20900%20children%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20under%20the%20rubble.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EIsraeli%20air%20strikes%20have%20killed%20over%20100%20children%20in%20Gaza%20every%20day%20since%20October%207.%20(In%20the%20first%20six%20days%20alone%2C%20Israel%20dropped%206%2C000%20bombs%20in%20Gaza%2C%20almost%20equalling%20the%20number%20of%20bombs%20dropped%20by%20the%20US%20in%20Afghanistan%20in%20one%20year.)%20UNICEF%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fapple-india-state-sponsored-spyware%5C%22%3Eputs%20the%20figure%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20children%20killed%20and%20injured%20daily%20at%20over%20400.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.savethechildren.net%2Fwhat-we-do%2Femergencies%2Fgaza-emergency%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20Save%20the%20Children%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20number%20of%20casualties%20among%20children%20in%20Gaza%20in%20three%20weeks%20%E2%80%9Csurpasses%20the%20annual%20number%20of%20children%20killed%20across%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20conflict%20zones%20since%202019%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EAnaesthesia%20shortages%20have%20meant%20that%20doctors%20ha