m%20wrong%20in%20calling%20him%20baby%20bowler).%20%3Cem%3EJab%20main%20team%20main%20aaya%20tha%2C%20main%20bhi%20bachcha%20tha%20Wasim%20Akram%20ke%20samne%3C%2Fem%3E%20(When%20I%20came%20into%20the%20Pakistan%20team%2C%20I%20was%20also%20a%20baby%20in%20front%20of%20Wasim%20Akram)%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Razzaq.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Bumrah%20has%20often%20been%20compared%20with%20Pakistan's%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shaheen%20Afridi%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108785-shaheen-afridi-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShaheen%20Afridi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20former%20Pakistan%20pace%20great%20Wasim%20Akram%20seems%20to%20have%20completely%20ended%20that%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20the%20best%20in%20the%20world%20right%20now.%20Top%20of%20the%20ladder!%20The%20control%2C%20the%20pace%2C%20the%20variations%2C%20just%20a%20complete%20bowler.%20A%20treat%20to%20watch.%20With%20the%20new%20ball%2C%20to%20get%20this%20kind%20of%20movement%20on%20this%20kind%20of%20pitch%20...%20pace%2C%20carry%2C%20follow-through...%20you%20name%20it%20he's%20a%20complete%20bowler%2C%26quot%3B%20Wasim%20said%20in%20a%20chat%20on%20A-Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698822600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F6n7jtsr_jasprit-bumrah-afp_625x300_04_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fcricket-world-cup-why-should-i-not-call-jasprit-bumrah-baby-bowler-ex-pakistan-star-justifies-strange-statement-4532526%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ex-Pakistan%20Allrounder%20Abdul%20Razzaq%20was%20asked%20a%20question%20on%20a%20TV%20show%20regarding%20an%20old%20comment%20of%20his%20where%20he%20called%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20a%20'baby%20bowler'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fcricket-world-cup-why-should-i-not-call-jasprit-bumrah-baby-bowler-ex-pakistan-star-