%20Hearing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%20has%20claimed%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20ethics%20committee%20that%20is%20looking%20into%20the%20cash-for-query%20controversy%20does%20not%20have%20powers%20to%20examine%20allegations%20of%20alleged%20criminality.%20She%20released%20her%20response%20today%20that%20she%20had%20prepped%20to%20give%20to%20the%20committee%20tomorrow%20when%20she%20appears%20before%20them.%20This%2C%20Ms%20Moitra%20said%2C%20was%20because%20the%20%26quot%3Bethics%20committee%20deemed%20it%20fit%20to%20release%20my%20summons%20to%20the%20media...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20I%20think%20it%20is%20important%20that%20I%20too%20release%20my%20letter%20to%20the%20committee%20before%20the%20'hearing'%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Moitra%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20committee%20chairperson%20Vinod%20Kumar%20Sonkar%2C%20Ms%20Moitra%20claimed%20the%20absence%20of%20this%20power%20was%20deliberately%20kept%20that%20way%20by%20%26quot%3Bour%20nation's%20founders%26quot%3B%20to%20prevent%20misuse%20of%20committees%20by%20government%20that%20enjoy%20brute%20majority%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20repeated%20her%20demand%20to%20cross-examine%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani.%20The%20businessman%20has%20alleged%20Ms%20Moitra%20took%20questions%20from%20him%20to%20ask%20in%20parliament%2C%20and%20also%20admitted%20he%20used%20Ms%20Moitra's%20parliamentary%20login%20ID%20and%20password%20to%20post%20questions%20from%20Dubai%20-%20a%20situation%2C%20if%20proved%2C%20will%20mean%20a%20breach%20of%20privilege%20and%20lead%20to%20her%20suspension%20from%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20post%20on%20X%20today%2C%20Ms%20Moitra%20said%20the%20parliamentary%20ethics%20committee%20may%20not%20be%20the%20%26quot%3Bappropriate%20forum%20to%20examine%20allegations%20of%20alleged%20criminality%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wish%20to%20respectfully%20remind%20you%20that%20parliamentary%20committees%20do%20not%20have%20criminal%20jurisdiction%20and%20have%20no%20mandate%20to%20investigate%20alleged%20criminality.%20This%20can%20only%20be%20done%20by%20law%20enforcement%20agencies.%20This%20check%20was%20specifically%20created%20by%20our%20nation's%20founders%20to%20prevent%20the%20slightest%20misuse%20of%20committees%20by%20governments%20enjoying%20a%20brute%20majority%20in%20parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Moitra%20said%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20ethics%20committee%20chairperson%20Vinod%20Kumar%20Sonkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESince%20Ethics%20Committee%20deemed%20it%20fit%20to%20release%20my%20summons%20to%20the%20media%20I%20think%20it%20is%20important%20I%20too%20release%20my%20letter%20to%20the%20Committee%20before%20my%20%26quot%3Bhearing%26quot%3B%20tomorrow.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FA8MwFRsImk%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FA8MwFRsImk%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Mahua%20Moitra%20(%40MahuaMoitra)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMahuaMoitra%2Fstatus%2F1719556716382097530%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%201%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3ESupreme%20Court%20lawyer%20Jai%20Anant%20Dehadrai%2C%20on%20whose%20complaint%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20the%20entire%20case%20rests%2C%20was%20cross-examined%20by%20the%20ethics%20committee%20on%20October%2026%2C%20while%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%2C%20who%20led%20the%20call%20to%20investigate%20the%20allegation%20that%20Ms%20Moitra%20gave%20her%20parliament%20login%20ID%20to%20the%20businessman%2C%20was%20allowed%20to%20explain%20his%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20CBI%20complaint%2C%20Mr%20Dubey%20had%20written%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20and%20levelled%20cash-for-query%20allegations%20against%20Ms%20Moitra.%20The%20Trinamool%20MP%20has%20called%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20lawyer%20her%20%26quot%3Bjilted%20ex%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%2C%20one%20of%20the%20fiercest%20critics%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20will%20appear%20before%20the%20ethics%20committee%20tomorrow.%20She%20asked%20the%20committee%20to%20ensure%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bno%20room%20for%20political%20partisanship%26quot%3B%20in%20their%20functioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20alleged%20the%20committee%20has%20not%20made%20any%20code%20of%20conduct%20for%20MPs%20to%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20till%20date%20the%20committee%20on%20ethics%20has%20not%20formulated%20any%20code%20of%20conduct%20for%20members%20and%20in%20fact%20the%20committee%20has%20not%20even%20had%20any%20sittings%20in%20the%20past%20two%20years.%20I%20wish%20to%20most%20respectfully%20point%20out%20that%20in%20view%20of%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20structured%20code%20of%20conduct%2C%20it%20is%20all%20the%20more%20important%20that%20each%20case%20be%20dealt%20with%20in%20an%20objective%20and%20fair%20manner...%26quot%3B%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20said%20in%20the%20letter%20to%20the%20ethics%20committee%20chairperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ethics%20committee%20will%20give%20a%20report%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20%26quot%3Bas%20early%20as%20possible%26quot%3B%2C%20people%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20the%20matter%20told%20NDTV%20last%20week%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Pawan%20Bansal%20committee%20that%20gave%20its%20report%20in%20just%20two%20weeks%20in%20December%202005%20in%20the%20infamous%20cash-for-questions%20scam%20when%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20was%20in%20power%20in%20the%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698817620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F261uj8ag_mahua-moitra_650x400_28_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com