%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Ftvandshowbiz%2F24589399%2Frobbie-williams-plastic-surgery-treatment-manopause%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Sun%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mr%20Williams%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20hair%20is%20thinning%2C%20the%20testosterone%20has%20left%20the%20building%2C%20the%20serotonin%20is%20not%20really%20here%20and%20the%20dopamine%20said%20goodbye%20a%20long%20time%20ago.%20I've%20used%20up%20all%20of%20the%20natural%20good%20stuff.%20I've%20got%20the%20manopause.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20daughter%20says%20to%20me%2C%20'Daddy's%20lazy'.%20I%20don't%20like%20the%20term%20'lazy'%20as%20that's%20how%20I%20was%20described%20when%20I%20was%20younger.%20The%20reality%20is%20that%20I'm%20just%20f******%20knackered%20from%20what%20I%20did%20to%20myself%20in%20the%20Nineties%20and%20bits%20of%20the%202000s%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Williams%20is%20married%20to%20actor%20Ayda%20Field.%20He%20has%20been%20open%20about%20beating%20his%20addictions%20to%20food%20and%20drugs%20-%20especially%20to%20sleeping%20pill%20Zopiclone%20-%20after%20he%20left%20'Take%20That'.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20different%20sleep%20pattern%20to%20other%20people.%20I'm%20magnetically%20drawn%20to%204am%20and%20falling%20asleep%20at%20six%20and%20there's%20nothing%20I%20can%20do%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Williams.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20go%20to%20bed%20at%2011pm%20and%20I'm%20just%20lying%20there%20completely%20awake%20and%20completely%20alert%20until%205am.%20It's%20one%20of%20the%20banes%20of%20Ayda's%20existence%20that%20she%20doesn't%20get%20me%20until%201pm%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20singer%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20UK's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhs.uk%2Fconditions%2Fmale-menopause%2F%5C%22%3ENational%20Health%20Service%20(NHS)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BMale%20menopause%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20more%20common%20