f-fire-1235774825%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fmister-smith-entertainment-riddle-of-fire-1235774825%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fmister-smith-entertainment-riddle-of-fire-1235774825%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Analysis%3A%20Out%20On%20Bail%2C%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%20Moves%20On%20Political%20Chessboard%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20as%20though%20Diwali%20came%20a%20full%2012%20days%20ahead%20to%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20at%20least%20for%20supporters%20of%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20and%20admirers%20of%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Chandrababu%20Naidu.%20They%20burst%20firecrackers%20and%20distributed%20sweets%20to%20celebrate%20the%20return%20of%20their%20leader%2C%20after%2053%20days%20of%20being%20detained%20by%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20the%20news%20broke%2C%20scenes%20of%20celebrations%20on%20the%20streets%20across%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20came%20on%20TV%2C%20mostly%20on%20those%20channels%20seen%20as%20pro-Naidu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETill%20late%20night%20when%20Mr%20Naidu%20undertook%20that%20road%20journey%20from%20Rajahmundry%20Central%20Jail%20to%20his%20home%20in%20Guntur's%20Undavalli%2C%20big%20crowds%20were%20gathered%20all%20along%20to%20get%20a%20glimpse%20of%20their%20leader%2C%20greet%20him%20and%20show%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYou%20could%20dismiss%20the%20show%20of%20solidarity%20and%20support%20as%20appropriate%20political%20optics%20created%20by%20a%20party%20with%20a%20well-organised%20cadre%2C%20just%20about%20six%20months%20before%20the%20state%20election.%20Something%20that%20they%20perhaps%20failed%20to%20do%20to%20the%20same%20scale%20when%20Mr%20Naidu%20was%20sent%20to%20jail.%20Perhaps%2C%20TDP%20leaders%20and%20the%20party%20workers%20were%20at%20that%20time%20too%20shocked%20in%20disbelief%20that%20this%20could%20happen%20to%20their%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Naidu%20knows%20only%20too%20well%20that%20it%20is%20a%20temporary%20reprieve%20that%20he%20has%20got%20from%20the%20courts.%20A%20four-week%20conditional%20interim%20bail%20on%20medical%20grounds%20doesn't%20mean%20much%20in%20terms%20of%20clearing%20his%20name%20or%20giving%20him%20a%20moral%20high%20ground.%20He%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20%26quot%3Bsurrender%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20jail%20superintendent%20before%205%20pm%20on%20November%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20the%20YS%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20is%20ready%20with%20at%20least%20three%20more%20cases%20of%20alleged%20corruption%2C%20Fibrenet%20case%2C%20Inner%20Ring%20Road%20case%20and%20the%20latest%20liquor%20licence%20case%2C%20in%20which%20Mr%20Naidu%20has%20been%20named%20as%20an%20accused%20and%20the%20prosecution%20is%20pushing%20to%20get%20him%20arrested.%20Mr%20Naidu%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20pushed%20into%20a%20tight%20corner.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20comes%20with%20years%20of%20political%20experience.%20After%20joining%20student%20politics%20at%20Sri%20Venkateswara%20University%20in%20his%20early%2020s%2C%20Youth%20Congress%20in%201975%2C%20becoming%20the%20youngest%20MLA%20at%2028%2C%20minister%20at%2030%2C%20and%20then%20Chief%20Minister%20at%2045%2C%20playing%20a%20national%20role%20as%20United%20Front%20Convenor%2C%20lending%20support%20to%20the%20NDA%20as%20the%20fourth-largest%20party%20in%20the%20country%2C%20facing%20a%20crushing%20defeat%20in%202004%2C%20becoming%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20a%20bifurcated%20state%20in%202014%20and%20again%20losing%20power%20in%202018%2C%20Mr%20Naidu's%20political%20graph%20has%20seen%20several%20ups%20and%20downs.%20He%20is%20a%20master%20of%20the%20art%20of%20political%20survival.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20seasoned%20politician%2C%20he%20knows%20he%20has%20to%20play%20the%20game%20by%20its%20rules.%20At%2073%2C%20age%20is%20no%20longer%20on%20his%20side%2C%20and%20he%20has%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20every%20little%20window%20of%20opportunity.%20Because%20his%20best%20chance%20in%20this%20latest%20battle%20is%20to%20make%20a%20political%20comeback%20in%202024%20by%20winning%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20even%20though%20Mr%20Naidu%20was%20released%20on%20conditional%20bail%2C%20with%20the%20government%20trying%20to%20ensure%20that%20restrictions%20were%20placed%20on%20his%20political%20activity%2C%20the%20veteran%20politician%20used%20the%20opportunity%20to%20pitch%20himself%20in%20the%20best%20manner%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20optics%20were%20right%2C%20with%20supporters%20euphoric%20about%20the%20return%20of%20their%20leader.%20The%20endearing%20visual%20of%20a%20senior%20politician%20visibly%20joyful%20at%20meeting%20his%20only%20grandson%20was%20a%20bonus%20that%20added%20a%20personalised%20human%20element%20to%20the%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20conditions%20imposed%20by%20the%20court%20and%20the%20multiple%2C%20repeated%20attempts%20after%20which%20Mr%20Naidu%20got%20bail%2C%20there%20was%20some%20doubt%20if%20he%20would%20risk%20making%20a%20political%20speech.%20But%20the%20politician%20made%20a%20speech%2C%20driving%20home%20his%20message%2C%20while%20steering%20clear%20of%20legal%20controversy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20on%20the%20face%20of%20it%2C%20it%20appeared%20like%20a%20speech%20to%20thank%20those%20who%20had%20come%20to%20greet%20him%2C%20it%20was%20a%20politically%20loaded%20speech%2C%20that%20Mr%20Naidu%20used%20to%20tell%20people%20he%20has%20been%20a%20man%20of%20integrity%2C%20respected%20and%20loved%20by%20people%20for%20his%20work%2C%20has%20friends%20across%20the%20political%20spectrum%2C%20is%20supported%20and%20well-regarded%20by%20political%20peers%2C%20with%20a%20stature%20far%20beyond%20the%20politics%20of%20the%20state.%20That%20is%20what%20Mr%20Naidu%20sought%20to%20convey.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20my%2045%20years%20of%20political%20life%2C%20I%20have%20done%20no%20wrong%20and%20I%20do%20not%20allow%20others%20to%20do%20wrong%20either%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20politician%20in%20his%20lifetime%20can%20experience%20this.%20I%20am%20grateful%20that%20people%20remember%20me%20for%20the%20development%20work%20that%20I%20have%20done%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20for%20building%20Hitech%20City%20in%20Hyderabad%2025%20years%20ago.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAm%20grateful%20for%20the%20overwhelming%20support%20of%20people%20not%20just%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%2C%20but%20across%20India%20and%20worldwide%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Naudi%20said.%20%26quot%3BJana%20Sena%20came%20out%20and%20openly%20supported%20us.%20We%20also%20got%20support%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20BRS%2C%20CPI%20and%20even%20the%20Congress.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EApparently%20cold-shouldered%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20his%20attempts%20to%20cosy%20up%20to%20the%20NDA%20in%20the%20preceding%20months%2C%20Mr%20Naidu%20wanted%20to%20convey%20that%20his%20political%20options%20were%20open%20and%20he%20has%20friends%20in%20places%20that%20matter%20and%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20elections%20just%20six%20months%20away%2C%20Mr%20Naidu%20needs%20to%20keep%20his%20leaders%20and%20party%20workers%20enthused%2C%20motivated%2C%20energised%2C%20with%20the%20confidence%20that%20victory%20is%20just%20a%20political%20fight%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20why%2C%20in%20his%20absence%2C%20Mr%20Naidu%20got%20his%20wife%20Bhuvaneswari%20and%20daughter-in-law%20Brahmani%2C%20both%20of%20whom%20have%20never%20been%20in%20the%20political%20limelight%2C%20to%20take%20the%20centre-stage%20and%20keep%20the%20party's%20political%20activity%20buzzing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt's%20another%20matter%20that%20Ms%20Bhuvaneswari's%20'Nijam%20Gelavali'%20(truth%20must%20win%20or%20prevail)%20yatra%20seems%20eerily%20like%20the%20'Odarpu%20Yatra'.%20As%20part%20of%20Nijam%20Gelavali%2C%20Ms%20Bhuvaneswari%20meets%20about%20150%20families%20who%20lost%20a%20family%20member%20because%20of%20the%20shock%20of%20Mr%20Naidu%20going%20to%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20death%20of%20YS%20Rajasekhar%20Reddy%20in%202009%2C%20YS%20Jagan%20Reddy%20had%20started%20'Odarpu%20Yatra'%20to%20console%20those%20who%20lost%20a%20family%20member%20because%20of%20the%20shock%20of%20the%20sudden%20death%20of%20YSR.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20TDP%20obviously%20saw%20the%20value%20of%20political%20mobilisation%2C%20appealing%20to%20personal%20emotions%20and%20linking%20them%20to%20the%20leader%20and%20the%20political%20party%2C%20so%20people%20see%20value%20beyond%20mere%20votes%20and%20politics%20in%20the%20association.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20meetings%20with%20the%20families%2C%20a%20public%20meeting%20and%20interaction%20became%20experience-gaining%20public%20platforms%20for%20a%20political%20novice%20like%20Ms%20Bhuvaneswari.%20The%20curiosity%20factor%20is%20an%20added%20attraction%20for%20the%20party%20cadre%20and%20others%2C%20who%20saw%20it's%20their%20responsibility%20to%20keep%20the%20party%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20as%20a%20relevant%20and%20viable%20political%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Telugu%20Desam%20and%20Jana%20Sena%20were%20appearing%20visibly%20together%20in%20these%20political%20activities%2C%20telling%20people%20that%20the%20chemistry%20works%2C%20with%20each%20bringing%20their%20strengths%20to%20the%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20%26quot%3Bthanksgiving%26quot%3B%20visit%20to%20Tirumala-Tirupati%2C%20Mr%20Naidu%20is%20expected%20to%20spend%20time%20away%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20getting%20operated%20for%20cataract%20at%20LV%20Prasad%20Eye%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20he%20stays%20away%20from%20the%20prying%20eyes%20of%20the%20intelligence%20establishment%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20while%20he%20sets%20his%20eyes%20and%20keeps%20his%20vision%20focussed%20on%20the%20target%3A%20the%202024%20assembly%20and%20parliament%20elections%20in%20Andhra%20Prades