sm%20and%20arson.%20Beed%20was%20the%20worst%20affected%20in%20the%20recent%20violence%20with%20two%20legislators'%20houses%20and%20a%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20office%20set%20on%20fire%20by%20the%20angry%20protesters.%20But%20the%20demand%20for%20Maratha%20reservations%20is%20not%20new%20to%20Maharashtra.%20In%20this%20article%2C%20we%20explain%20the%20reason%20behind%20this%20recent%20flare-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20Maratha%20Quota%20Demand%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EMarathas%2C%20who%20constitute%20nearly%2033%25%20of%20the%20state's%20population%2C%20have%20been%20demanding%20the%20reservation%20in%20education%20and%20government%20jobs.%20The%20first%20protest%20demanding%20reservation%20was%20held%20in%20Mumbai%20in%201982%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Mathadi%20Labour%20Union%20leader%20Annasaheb%20Patil.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20struck%20down%20Maharashtra's%20Socially%20and%20Educationally%20Backward%20Classes%20Act%2C%202018%2C%20which%20granted%20reservation%20to%20the%20Maratha%20community%2C%20for%20violating%20the%2050%20per%20cent%20quota%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20community%20has%20been%20seeking%20Kunbi%20caste%20certificates%20for%20Marathas%20which%20will%20enable%20their%20inclusion%20in%20the%20OBC%20category%20for%20reservation.%20Kunbis%2C%20who%20are%20associated%20with%20agriculture%2C%20are%20grouped%20under%20the%20OBC%20(Other%20Backward%20Classes)%20category%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20had%20formed%20a%20committee%20led%20by%20a%20retired%20judge%20to%20look%20into%20this%20demand.%20After%20examining%20the%20documents%20of%20a%20lakh%20people%2C%20about%2011%2C530%20Marathas%20were%20found%20to%20have%20documents%20of%20being%20Kunbi%2C%20the%20committee%20has%20said%20in%20its%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20called%20an%20all-party%20meeting%20on%20Wednesday%20to%20discuss%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20state%20amid%20the%20violent%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERecent%20flare-up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20fresh%20protests%20began%20after%20pro-quota%20activist%20Manoj%20Jarange%20Patil%20started%20an%20indefinite%20hunger%20strike%20on%20October%2025.%20He%20took%20few%20sips%20of%20water%20on%20Monday%20after%20being%20prodded%20by%20the%20locals%2C%20but%20his%20hunger%20strike%20is%20still%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Shinde%20on%20Tuesday%20dialled%20Mr%20Patil%20and%20assured%20him%20of%20a%20concrete%20decision%20by%20the%20state%20cabinet%20on%20giving%20Kunbi%20certificates%20to%20the%20Maratha%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20violences%20targeted%20mainly%20the%20NCP%20legislators%20and%20offices%20over%20some%20alleged%20comments%20by%20a%20politician%20on%20the%20quota%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENCP%20MLA%20Prakash%20Solanke%2C%20whose%20house%20was%20vandalized%20and%20set%20on%20fire%20in%20Beed%2C%20was%20purportedly%20heard%20calling%20the%20quota%20demand%20a%20%26quot%3Bchild's%20game%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20widely%20circulated%20audio%20clip.%20%26quot%3BThe%20person%20who%20has%20not%20even%20contested%20a%20gram%20panchayat%20election%20(seen%20as%20a%20dig%20at%20Manoj%20Patil)%2C%20has%20become%20a%20smart%20person%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20allegedly%20said%20in%20the%20clip.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFormer%20Chief%20Minister%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20has%20demanded%20the%20centre%20to%20resolve%20the%20issue%20of%20Maratha%20reservation%20by%20calling%20a%20special%20session%20of%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698815580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fp6iejmog_maratha-quota-violence-beed-ani_625x300_01_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-latest-flare-up-in-maharashtra-over-maratha-quota-demand-4533811%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maharashtra%20is%20witnessing%20a%20fresh%20wave%20of%20prot