o%20specific%20details%20of%20which%20government%20or%20agency%20was%20doing%20the%20targeting%2C%20nor%20did%20it%20describe%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20remote%20compromise%20being%20effected.%20However%2C%20the%20general%20description%20it%20provided%20was%20graphic%20enough%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20attackers%20are%20likely%20targeting%20you%20individually%20because%20of%20who%20you%20are%20or%20what%20you%20do.%20If%20your%20device%20is%20compromised%20by%20a%20state-sponsored%20attacker%2C%20they%20may%20be%20able%20to%20remotely%20access%20your%20sensitive%20data%2C%20communications%2C%20or%20even%20the%20camera%20and%20microphone.%20While%20it%E2%80%99s%20possible%20this%20is%20a%20false%20alarm%2C%20please%20take%20this%20warning%20seriously.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20previously%20targeted%20with%20the%20Israeli%20spyware%20Pegasus%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.ph%2FkLLsr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20was%20among%20several%20journalists%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20whose%20phone%20the%20spyware%20was%20found%20%E2%80%93%20receiving%20Apple%E2%80%99s%20alert%20(as%20I%20did)%20was%20a%20reminder%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20ingenuity%20in%20snooping%20on%20those%20it%20classifies%20as%20opponents.%20And%20of%20the%20ever%20evolving%20nature%20of%20spyware%2C%20malware%20and%20surveillance%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20is%20this%20a%20warning%20that%20Pegasus%20is%20being%20used%20again%3F%20Or%20perhaps%20some%20other%20spyware%20like%20Predator%3F%20At%20this%20stage%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpyware%20is%20big%20business%20globally%20and%20there%20are%20dozens%20of%20countries%20whose%20political%2C%20legal%20and%20ethical%20norms%20have%20created%20a%20permissive%20environment%20for%20ruling%20parties%20to%20weaponise%20surveillance%20for%20their%20own%20narrow%20partisan%20aims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIs%20there%20a%20parallel%20with%20Pegasus%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20Pegasus%20Project%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftag%2Fpegasus-project%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eof%20which%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%20was%20the%20India%20partner%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20used%20a%20leaked%20database%20of%20likely%20Pegasus%20victims%20to%20report%20on%20the%20targeting%20of%20thousands%20of%20individuals%20across%20dozens%20of%20countries%20by%20unidentified%20government%20clients%20of%20the%20Israeli%20spyware%20manufacturer%20NSO.%20Analysis%20of%20the%20numbers%20yielded%20geographical%20clusters%20and%20helped%20pinpoint%20the%20governments%20most%20likely%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%20and%20its%20partners%20were%20able%20to%20identify%20more%20than%20140%20likely%20targets%20of%20Pegasus%20and%20were%20able%20to%20confirm%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20spyware%20on%20the%20phones%20of%20over%20a%20dozen%20individuals.%20Among%20these%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftag%2Fpegasus-project%23%3A~%3Atext%3DPegasus%2520Project%2520Day%25202%253A%2520Rahul%2520Gandhi%252C%2520Prashant%2520Kishor%252C%2520Ashok%2520Lavasa%252C%2520Ashwini%2520Vaishnaw%252C%2520Prahlad%2520Patel%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20politician%20Prashant%20Kishor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whose%20phone%20yielded%20evidence%20of%20a%20compromise%20even%20as%20he%20was%20guiding%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20its%20election%20battle%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20nature%20and%20spread%20of%20the%20Indian%20targets%20on%20the%20leaked%20Pegasus%20database%2C%20it%20was%20evident%20that%20the%20targeting%20client%20was%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAre%20the%20%E2%80%9Cstate-sponsored%20attackers%E2%80%9D%20this%20time%20also%20Indian%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2Fclarification%20emailed%20to%20reporters%20on%20Tuesday%20after%20several%20opposition%20leaders%20blamed%20the%20Modi%20government%20for%20targeting%20them%2C%20Apple%20said%20that%20it%20%E2%80%9Cdoes%20not%20attribute%20the%20threat%20notifications%20to%20any%20specific%20state-sponsored%20attacker.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%202021%2C%20when%20it%20enabled%20the%20threat%20notification%20feature%2C%20Apple%20has%20sent%20similar%20alerts%20to%20persons%20in%20150%20countries%20around%20the%20world.%20What%20this%20means%20is%20that%20Apple%20has%20detected%20targeting%20attempts%20by%20multiple%20governments%2C%20at%20different%20points%20in%20time%2C%20and%20has%20sent%20out%20alerts%20to%20the%20affected%20individuals.%20In%20none%20of%20those%20cases%20has%20Apple%20identified%20the%20state-sponsor%20of%20the%20attack%20but%20it%20never%20really%20needed%20to.%20Thus%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Felfaro.net%2Fen%2F202111%2Fel_salvador%2F0000025862-apple-warns-journalists-of-state-surveillance-in-el-salvador%3Fu%3Dst-full_text%3Dall%26tpl%3D11%26utm_source%3Dfarotext%26utm_medium%3Dinitdocu%26utm_campaign%3Dtext-0000025862_apple-warns-journalists-of-state-surveillance-in-el-salvador%23%3A~%3Atext%3DU.S.%2520tech%2520giant%2520Apple%2520alerted%2Cgovernment%2520surveillance%2520of%2520their%2520iPhones.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewhen%20two%20dozen%20journalists%20in%20El%20Salvador%20received%20warnings%20about%20state%20actors%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20attempting%20to%20compromise%20their%20iPhones%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20as%20day%20that%20the%20targeting%20state%20was%20the%20government%20of%20El%20Salvador.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGovernment%20handlers%20have%20predictably%20clutched%20at%20the%20straw%20of%20understatement%20offered%20by%20Apple%E2%80%99s%20clarification%20to%20suggest%20there%20is%20some%20ambiguity%20about%20who%20might%20have%20targeted%20India%E2%80%99s%20opposition%20leaders.%20But%20as%20in%20the%20case%20of%20the%20Pegasus%20database%20of%20Indian%20numbers%2C%20it%20is%20only%20the%20Indian%20government%20which%20would%20have%20an%20interest%20in%20deploying%20spyware%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpegasus-spyware-india-modi-quadream-cognyte%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecosting%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20range%20of%20targets%20that%20we%20have%20seen%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhy%20did%20Apple%20say%20some%20of%20its%20threat%20notifications%20may%20be%20%E2%80%98false%20alarms%E2%80%99%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98false%20alarm%E2%80%99%20suggestion%20has%20predictably%20been%20played%20up%20by%20a%20section%20of%20the%20media%20eager%20to%20bat%20for%20the%20Modi%20government%20without%20any%20reference%20to%20what%20Apple%20is%20actually%20trying%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01030924%2FF9wMz85bsAAPzGU.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01030924%2FF9wMz85bsAAPzGU.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01030924%2FF9wMz85bsAAPzGU-300x168.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01030924%2FF9wMz85bsAAPzGU-1024x573.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682850%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22672%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENDTV%20breaking%20news%20flash%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20words%20being%20quoted%20above%20is%20only%20a%20part%20of%20what%20Apple%20said%20in%20its%20statement%20and%20has%20actually%20been%20up%20on%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20website%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fen-in%2F102174%23%3A~%3Atext%3DApple%2520threat%2520notifications%2520will%2520never%2Cto%2520appleid.apple.com%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efor%20several%20months%20now.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0It%20notes%20that%20the%20sophisticated%20nature%20of%20the%20attacks%20make%20their%20detection%20difficult%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CState-sponsored%20attackers%20are%20very%20well-funded%20and%20sophisticated%2C%20and%20their%20attacks%20evolve%20over%20time.%20Detecting%20such%20attacks%20relies%20on%20threat%20intelligence%20signals%20that%20are%20often%20imperfect%20and%20incomplete.%20It%E2%80%99s%20possible%20that%20some%20Apple%20threat%20notifications%20may%20be%20false%20alarms%2C%20or%20that%20some%20attacks%20are%20not%20detected.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20anything%2C%20Apple%20is%20reinforcing%20the%20danger%20posed%20by%20state-sponsored%20attackers.%20Which%20is%20why%20the%20message%20it%20sent%20each%20of%20the%20victims%20on%20Monday%20night%20had%20this%20warning%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20it%E2%80%99s%20possible%20this%20is%20a%20false%20alarm%2C%20%3Ci%3Eplease%20take%20this%20warning%20seriously%3C%2Fi%3E.%E2%80%9D%20(Emphasis%20added)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDid%20Apple%20help%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20attempts%20at%20damage%20control%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20opposition%20politicians%20took%20to%20Twitter%20one%20after%20the%20other%20on%20Tuesday%20morning%20to%20draw%20attention%20to%20the%20alerts%20they%20had%20received%20from%20Apple%2C%20the%20needle%20of%20suspicion%20clearly%20pointed%20towards%20the%20Modi%20government.%20The%20government%E2%80%99s%20first%20attempt%20at%20damage%20control%20was%20to%20float%20the%20suggestion%20via%20friendly%20journalists%20that%20these%20alerts%20had%20somehow%20been%20sent%20out%20in%20error.%20A%20number%20of%20television%20anchors%20started%20sharing%20a%20forward%20they%20had%20been%20sent%20claiming%20that%20%E2%80%98sources%20in%20Apple%E2%80%99%20had%20said%20an%20%E2%80%9Calgorithm%20malfunction%20triggered%20these%20mails%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20the%20company%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20issue%20a%20statement%20in%20this%20regard%20in%20sometime.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20an%20example%20of%20one%20of%20these%20messages%20being%20shared%20at%2012%3A16.%20Journalists%20with%20whom%20this%20was%20shared%20have%20said%20off%20the%20record%20that%20they%20received%20this%20%E2%80%98algorithm%20malfunction%E2%80%99%20advisory%20from%20a%20senior%20government%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01031625%2FScreenshot-2023-11-01-at-3.15.22-AM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22783%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01031625%2FScreenshot-2023-11-01-at-3.15.22-AM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01031625%2FScreenshot-2023-11-01-at-3.15.22-AM-300x188.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01031625%2FScreenshot-2023-11-01-at-3.15.22-AM-1024x640.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682853%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22489%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAround%201%20pm%2C%20Apple%E2%80%99s%20India%20team%20indeed%20put%20out%20a%20%E2%80%98clarification%E2%80%99%20and%20though%20it%20did%20not%20cite%20the%20(absurd)%20algorithm%20malfunction%20theory%2C%20it%20highlighted%20two%20pieces%20of%20information%20that%20the%20government%20was%20quick%20to%20latch%20on%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20none%20of%20those%20who%20had%20received%20the%20alert%20the%20previous%20night%20and%20who%20had%20contacted%20Apple%20for%20more%20information%20and%20help%20in%20dealing%20with%20the%20threat%20received%20any%20response.%20But%20the%20company%20was%20quick%20to%20issue%20a%20statement%20which%20began%20with%20the%20declaration%3A%20%E2%80%9CApple%20does%20not%20attribute%20the%20threat%20notifications%20to%20any%20specific%20state-sponsored%20attacker.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%20contacted%20Apple%20India%E2%80%99s%20team%20to%20ask%20about%20the%20%E2%80%98algorithm%20malfunction%E2%80%99%20theory%2C%20their%20reply%20was%20categorical%3A%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20untrue%20and%20we%20do%20not%20know%20where%20this%20came%20from%E2%80%A6%20We%E2%80%99re%20advising%20all%20reporters%20the%20same%20on%20background.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20we%20analyse%20Apple%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98clarification%E2%80%99%20and%20its%20impact%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20minister%20in%20government%20knew%20the%20company%20was%20going%20to%20%E2%80%9Cissue%20a%20statement%20in%20this%20regard%20in%20sometime%E2%80%9D%20makes%20two%20things%20clear.%20First%2C%20that%20it%20was%20the%20Modi%20government%20which%20was%20keen%20for%20Apple%20to%20say%20something%20on%20the%20subject.%20And%20second%2C%20that%20there%20was%20likely%20some%20process%20of%20negotiation%20between%20the%20government%20and%20Apple%20about%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98clarification%E2%80%99.%20Perhaps%20this%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20the%20Apple%20representative%20repeatedly%20told%20journalists%20to%20whom%20the%20%E2%80%98clarification%E2%80%99%20was%20sent%20(including%20to%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E)%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20be%20really%20helpful%20if%20you%20can%20note%20the%20150%20countries%C2%A0statistic%20in%20your%20story%2C%C2%A0found%20in%20the%20on%20background%20info%20below.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Apple%20statement%E2%80%99s%20reference%20to%20150%20countries%20was%20for%20the%20period%20since%202021%20but%20the%20way%20IT%20minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20recounted%20it%2C%20it%20was%20as%20if%20Apple%20had%20alerted%20people%20in%20150%20countries%20at%20the%20very%20same%20time%20as%20they%20had%20contacted%20those%20in%20India.%20This%20is%20what%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1719282293414707396%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20minister%20told%20the%20media%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20ANI%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CApple%20has%20released%20a%20clarification%20that%20the%20allegations%20by%20compulsive%20critics%20are%20not%20true.%20Such%20advisories%20have%20been%20sent%20to%20people%20in%20150%20countries.%20The%20people%20who%20cannot%20see%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20country%20are%20doing%20destructive%20politics%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%20creating%20the%20impression%20that%20the%20opposition%20politicians%20who%20had%20received%20the%20%E2%80%98state-sponsored%20attack%E2%80%99%20alerts%20from%20Apple%20were%20part%20of%20a%20common%20group%20spread%20across%20150%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20all%20of%20whom%20had%20been%20informed%20at%20the%20same%20time%20%E2%80%93%20Vaishnaw%20was%20trying%20to%20shift%20the%20blame%20away%20from%20his%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20reality%2C%20Apple%20launched%20its%20threat%20notifications%20process%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.the-sun.com%2Ftech%2F4161369%2Fapple-iphone-urgent-warning-biggest-hack-history-undetected%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20November%202021%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20response%20to%20reporting%20by%20the%20Pegasus%20Project.%20The%20first%20time%20Apple%20used%20the%20%E2%80%9C150%20countries%E2%80%9D%20figure%20was%20in%20July%202022%2C%20when%20it%20became%20aware%20of%20a%20new%20vulnerability%20in%20the%20iPhone%20that%20was%20serious%20enough%20for%20it%20to%20introduce%20the%20%E2%80%98lockdown%20mode%E2%80%99%20as%20a%20security%20feature%20and%20notify%20people%20around%20the%20world%20who%20might%20have%20been%20targeted%20through%20an%20iMessage%20exploit.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Ftechnology%2F2022%2F07%2F06%2Fapple-spyware-lockdown-pegasus%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20Washington%20Post%20reported%20at%20the%20time%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CResearchers%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Toronto%E2%80%99s%20Citizen%20Lab%20captured%20what%20they%20said%20was%20a%20new%20version%20of%20Pegasus%20last%20year%20that%20exploited%20Apple%20devices%20through%20iMessage%20without%20needing%20any%20action%20from%20the%20victim%20to%20be%20installed.%20That%20triggered%20an%20Apple%20investigation%20and%20the%20notifications%20to%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20a%20call%20with%20reporters%20Tuesday%2C%20Apple%20representatives%20said%20those%20warnings%20have%20now%20gone%20to%20residents%20of%20150%20countries%2C%20underscoring%20the%20dramatic%20scale%20of%20the%20problem.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAre%20Apple%E2%80%99s%20warnings%20%E2%80%98vague%E2%80%99%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20IT%20minister%20has%20sought%20to%20make%20light%20of%20the%20emerging%20surveillance%20scandal%20by%20presenting%20Apple%E2%80%99s%20alert%20as%20%E2%80%9Cvague%E2%80%9D%20because%20it%20lacks%20specifics.%20But%20this%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Indian%20phone%20users%20have%20been%20alerted%20to%20the%20possible%20use%20of%20spyware%20against%20them.%20In%202018%2C%20WhatsApp%20wrote%20to%20two%20dozen%20people%20alerting%20them%20to%20the%20danger.%20In%202021%2C%20when%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fi%3Eanalysed%20the%20leaked%20Pegasus%20database%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Frevealed-how-the-wire-partners-cracked-pegasus-project-implications-india%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eit%20found%20the%20numbers%20of%20many%20of%20those%20whom%20WhatsApp%20had%20contacted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20spyware%20payloads%20are%20delivered%20through%20messaging%20vectors%2C%20it%20stands%20to%20reason%20that%20Apple%2C%20which%20has%20the%20ability%20to%20detect%20anomalies%20in%20the%20use%20of%20Apple%20IDs%2C%20iMessages%20and%20FaceTime%20calls%2C%20would%20be%20in%20the%20same%20position%20as%20WhatsApp%20was%20when%20it%20sounded%20the%20alarm%20five%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20happens%20next%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Apple%20may%20indeed%20have%20notified%20people%20across%20150%20countries%20over%20the%20past%20two%20years%20about%20hacking%20attempts%20on%20their%20phones%2C%20what%20it%20did%20on%20Monday%20night%20was%20to%20inform%20a%20group%20of%20opposition%20politicians%20and%20journalists%20in%20India%20whose%20vulnerability%20had%20presumably%20just%20come%20to%20light%20thanks%20to%20the%20activities%20of%20%E2%80%9Cstate-sponsored%20attackers%E2%80%9D.%20Which%20brings%20us%20back%20to%20the%20beginning%3A%20Who%20are%20these%20attackers%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVaishnaw%20has%20said%20his%20government%20will%20probe%20these%20attacks%20and%20wants%20both%20Apple%20and%20the%20individuals%20it%20contacted%20to%20cooperate%20with%20it.%20Apple%20has%20said%20repeatedly%20that%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cunable%20to%20provide%20more%20information%20about%20what%20caused%20us%20to%20send%20%E2%80%A6%20this%20notification%2C%20as%20that%20may%20help%20state-sponsored%20attackers%20adapt%20their%20behavior%20to%20evade%20detection%20in%20the%20future.%E2%80%9D%20This%20means%20Apple%2C%20which%20probably%20knows%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20it%20has%20revealed%2C%20will%20not%20willingly%20come%20forward%20with%20more%20information.%20Nor%20is%20the%20Modi%20government%20likely%20to%20use%20whatever%20coercive%20powers%20it%20has%20in%20its%20arsenal%20to%20compel%20Apple%20to%20reveal%20what%20it%20knows%20because%20the%20information%20which%20emerges%20will%20likely%20damage%20it%20even%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20back%20to%20the%20same%20impasse%20last%20seen%20over%20Pegasus%2C%20where%20the%20government%20neither%20confirmed%20nor%20denied%20its%20use%20of%20the%20spyware%20and%20defied%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20direction%20that%20it%20cooperate%20with%20the%20probe%20panel%20that%20was%20set%20up%20under%20Justice%20(retd)%20Raveendran.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20allowed%20the%20Raveendran%20report%20to%20be%20shelved%20and%20chose%20not%20to%20begin%20contempt%20proceedings%20against%20the%20government.%20But%20the%20latest%20alerts%20from%20Apple%20provide%20confirmation%20that%20the%20use%20of%20spyware%20as%20a%20means%20of%20illegal%20surveillance%20is%20still%20continuing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUsing%20spyware%20against%20political%20opponents%20is%20not%20only%20a%20violation%20of%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20privacy%20but%20also%20amounts%20to%20subversion%20of%20the%20electoral%20process.%20The%20fact%20that%20public%20money%20is%20spent%20acquiring%20spyware%20which%20is%20deployed%20to%20further%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20also%20makes%20this%20an%20offence%20under%20the%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3EPrevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act%20and%20the%20Representation%20of%20People%20Act.%20In%20the%20United%20States%2C%20President%20Richard%20Nixon%20was%20forced%20to%20resign%20over%20a%20surveillance%20operation%20that%20looks%20like%20a%20tea%20party%20compared%20to%20the%20high-tech%20intrusive%20attacks%20being%20used%20against%20the%20opposition%20in%20India.%20But%20in%20India%20for%20some%20reason%2C%20none%20of%20this%20seems%20to%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698798647000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01032150%2F921be743-4247-46a3-943b-a58037be65f3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmodi-government-in-damage-control-mode-as-apple-spyware-alert-revives-ghost-of-pegasus%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Here's%20what%20we%20know%20so%20far%20about%20Apple's%20warning%20that%20state-spons