h%20more%20than%20a%20traditional%20combustion-engine%20vehicle%20due%20to%20the%20weight%20of%20their%20battery.%20Musk's%20specs%20for%20the%20Cybertruck%20fall%20well%20within%20the%20range%20of%20a%20typical%20EV%20pickup%20truck.%20For%20comparison%2C%20the%20Ford%20Lightning%20weighs%20over%206%2C000%20pounds%20and%20the%20Rivian%20R1T%20weighs%20over%208%2C000%20pounds%2C%20according%20to%20their%20respective%20owners'%20manuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%3EMusk%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20said%20the%20company%20will%20offer%20a%20%26quot%3Bbeast%20mode%20version%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Cybertruck.%20Though%2C%20he%20did%20not%20specify%20what%20would%20be%20included%20in%20that%20version%20of%20the%20EV.%20In%20September%2C%20the%20billionaire%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FteslaownersSV%2Fstatus%2F1705053996572897477%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1705363066542493951%257Ctwgr%255E956f0d4517ac35d571afe90f0f363fbe2c341557%257Ctwcon%255Es2_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.teslarati.com%252Felon-musk-tesla-cybertruck-performance%252F%5C%22%3Esaid%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter%2C%20that%20there%20will%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bperformance%20Cybertruck%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20%26quot%3Bkicks%20ass.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tesla%20CEO%20also%20reiterated%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20the%20Cybertruck%20will%20have%20bulletproof%20steel%20panels%20and%20there%20will%20even%20be%20an%20option%20for%20people%20to%20purchase%20bulletproof%20glass%20for%20the%20vehicle%2C%20though%20that%20variant%20will%20pose%20a%20major%20usability%20tradeoff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20make%20anything%20bulletproof%20if%20you%20want%2C%20but%20the%20glass%20has%20to%20be%20very%20thick%20for%20be%20bulletproof%2C%20so%20it%20can't%20go%20up%20and%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20bulletproof%20windows%20will%20be%20immobile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20interview%2C%20Rogan%20even%20tested%20out%20the%20Cybertruck's%20exterior%20by%20shooting%20an%20arrow%20at%20the%20vehicle's%20stainless%20steel%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20the%20arrow%20appeared%20to%20partially%20break%20against%20the%20car's%20exterior%2C%20leaving%20a%20small%20dent%20in%20the%20side%20of%20the%20Cybertruck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221706%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joe%20Rogan%20shot%20an%20arrow%20at%20the%20Cybertruck.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65416c7536d588dc55c7585d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22959%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJoe%20Rogan%20shot%20an%20arrow%20at%20the%20Cybertruck.%3Cp%3EThe%20Joe%20Rogan%20Experience%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20there%20will%20be%20three%20demonstrations%20to%20prove%20the%20Cybertruck%20is%20bulletproof%2C%20including%20shooting%20the%20vehicle%20with%20a%20Tommy%20gun%2C%20a%2045%20milimeter%20shotgun%2C%20and%20a%209%20milimeter%20gun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrucks%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20tough%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Musk%20first%20revealed%20the%20Cybertruck%20in%202019%20he%20attempted%20to%20demonstrate%20the%20vehicle's%20%26quot%3Barmour%20glass%26quot%3B%20windows%20by%20having%20Tesla's%20design%20boss%20throw%20a%20metal%20ball%20at%20the%20Cybertruck's%20window.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20glass%20immediately%20broke%20on%20contact%20with%20the%20metal%20ball.%20Musk%20later%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1198772995021406209%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20social%20media%20that%20a%20prior%20test%20had%20compromised%20the%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSledgehammer%20impact%20on%20door%20cracked%20base%20of%20glass%2C%20which%20is%20why%20steel%20ball%20didn't%20bounce%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20wrote%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BShould%20have%20done%20steel%20ball%20on%20window%2C%20*then*%20sledgehammer%20the%20door.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Cybertruck%20wouldn't%20be%20the%20first%20car%20to%20have%20bulletproof%20glass%20windows%2C%20it's%20an%20unusual%20feature%20for%20a%20civilian%20vehicle.%20The%20thick%20windows%20can%20also%20contribute%20toward%20a%20very%20heavy%20vehicle.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.in%2Fslideshows%2Fmiscellaneous%2Fhow-the-the-kennedy-assassinatio%5B%E2%80%A6%5Dored-beast-used-by-trump-and-obama%2Fslidelist%2F71992924.cms%5C%22%3E2009%20Cadillac%20Presidential%20Limousine%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20former%20President%20Barack%20Obama%20rode%20to%20his%20inauguration%20had%20five-inch%20windows%20and%20eight-inch%20walls%20designed%20to%20protect%20him%20against%20all%20manner%20of%20weapons%20and%20weighed%20in%20at%20about%2010%20tons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20he's%20hoping%20for%20the%20%26quot%3BBeast%20Mode%26quot%3B%20version%20of%20the%20EV%20pickup%20to%20be%20able%20to%20go%20from%20zero%20to%2060%20miles%20per%20hour%20in%20under%203%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20looks%20so%20odd.%20You%20have%20to%20see%20it%20in%20the%20flesh%2C%26quot%3B%20Rogan%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20coolest%20looking%20fucking%20production%20car%20that's%20ever%20been%20made.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Tesla%20said%20there%20will%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-release-date-november-delivery-event-giga-texas-2023-10%5C%22%3Edelivery%20event%20for%20the%20Cybertruck%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20November%2030.%20But%2C%20Musk%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-earnings-q3-report-live-updates-guidance-analyst-call-stock-reaction-2023-10%23it-sounds-like-its-gonna-be-a-hellish-18-months-for-tesla-workers%5C%22%3Ewarned%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20will%20be%20difficult%20to%20scale%20production%20