es%20incur%20less%20debt%20than%20the%20national%20average%2C%20and%20far%20less%20than%20other%20private%20universities%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20continued.%20%26quot%3BRather%20than%20the%20Department%20protecting%20students%2C%20we%20are%20being%20forced%20to%20protect%20our%20students%20from%20this%20targeted%20and%20unwarranted%20government%20overreach.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGCU%20has%2020%20days%20to%20request%20a%20hearing%20on%20the%20fine%20or%20submit%20written%20material%20indicating%20why%20the%20fine%20should%20not%20be%20imposed.%20Along%20with%20the%20fine%2C%20the%20department%20is%20also%20enforcing%20specific%20conditions%20on%20the%20school%20to%20allow%20it%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Econtinue%20participating%20in%20federal%20student%20aid%20programs%2C%20including%20a%20requirement%20to%20inform%20students%20of%20the%20average%20total%20tuition%20and%20fees%20paid%20by%20graduates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20department%20official%20also%20noted%20to%20reporters%20on%20the%20press%20call%20that%20while%20this%20fine%20is%20an%20enforcement%20action%20against%20the%20school%2C%20borrowers%20who%20believe%20they%20were%20defrauded%20can%20also%20submit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupreme-court-upholds-student-loan-debt-cancellation-defrauded-borrowers-settlement-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eborrower%20defense%20claims%20for%20student-debt%20relief%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20department%20has%20taken%20action%20numerous%20times%20over%20the%20past%20year%20to%20provide%20relief%20to%20borrowers%20it%20says%20were%20defrauded%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-university-of-phoenix-debt-relief-education-ftc-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2437%20million%20to%20former%20University%20of%20Phoenix%20students%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeceptive%20for-profit%20graduate%20programs%20are%20a%20large%20and%20growing%2