d%20facilitate%20a%20smoother%20transition%20from%20school%20to%20the%20workforce.%20It%20operates%20in%2024%20states%20across%2072%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F274165%2Ftop-inspiring-indian-villages-sustainable-development%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edistricts%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMagic%20Bus%20has%20played%20a%20pioneering%20role%20in%20introducing%20sports-for-development%20and%20life%20skills%20education%20in%20India%20and%20Southeast%20Asia.%20%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20we%20empower%20individuals%20to%20acquire%20essential%20life%20skills%20through%20sports.%20By%20gathering%20on%20the%20playground%2C%20we%20especially%20empower%20girls%20to%20assert%20their%20presence%20in%20a%20domain%20traditionally%20reserved%20for%20boys.%20We%20aim%20to%20challenge%20gender%20stereotypes%2C%20encouraging%20girls%20to%20break%20barriers%20while%20fostering%20equal%20participation%20from%20boys%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jayant%20Rastogi%2C%20Global%20CEO%2C%20Magic%20Bus%20India%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20shows%20that%20adolescents%20in%20its%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.magicbus.org%2Fuploads%2Fpdf%2FMB_Impact%2520Report%252022-23.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20programmes%20improved%20their%20school%20regularity%20by%2021.8%25%2C%20a%2031%25%20increase%20in%20perceived%20self-efficacy%2C%20and%20a%2034.7%25%20boost%20in%20resilience.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22School%20boys%20being%20given%20a%20proper%20coaching%20for%20Cricket.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990-500x500.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990-150x150.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990-768x768.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990-96x96.jpeg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333297%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESchool%20boys%20are%20being%20given%20proper%20coaching%20for%20Cricket.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Baddi%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20place%20where%20Magic%20Bus%20has%20actively%20engaged%20since%202015%2C%20a%20significant%20milestone%20was%20reached%20in%20March%202021.%20The%20organisation%20introduced%20a%20sports%20programme%20exclusively%20tailored%20for%20girls.%20Divided%20into%20two%20distinct%20phases%20from%20December%202021%20to%20March%202023%2C%20this%20programme%20carries%20a%20primary%20objective%20of%20empowering%20girls%20aged%2011%20to%2018%20through%20the%20influence%20of%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Vivek%20Sharma%2C%20the%20programme%20manager%2C%2010%2C000%20girls%20were%20given%20sports%20sessions%20each%20in%20kabaddi%20or%20cricket.%20The%20girls%20also%20took%20part%20in%20tournaments%20within%20their%20schools.%20Some%20of%20them%20were%20then%20chosen%20to%20compete%20in%20district%2C%20state%2C%20and%20national%20tournaments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20objectives%20of%20the%20programme%20also%20include%20the%20holistic%20development%20of%20the%20participants%2C%20which%20includes%20communication%2C%20socio-emotional%20learning%2C%20and%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVivek%20says%20they%20were%20able%20to%20succeed%20in%20Baddi%20because%20Magic%20Bus%20had%20earned%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20trust%20first.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20been%20planning%20since%202015.%20We%20worked%20with%20the%20girls%2C%20the%20boys%20and%20their%20parents%20and%20sensitised%20them%20%5Bto%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20girls%E2%80%99%20sports%20programme%5D.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20programme%20has%20also%20actively%20addressed%20common%20concerns%20raised%20by%20parents%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F162218%2Fuber-cab-women-safety%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eregarding%20the%20safety%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20expenses%20of%20the%20girls%20participating%20in%20tournaments%20held%20in%20larger%20cities.%20Recognising%20these%20concerns%2C%20the%20programme%20takes%20responsibility%20for%20the%20girls%E2%80%99%20expenses%20and%20ensures%20their%20safety%20by%20arranging%20for%20accompanying%20coaches%20during%20their%20travel.%20In%20certain%20cases%2C%20the%20programme%20even%20covers%20medical%20expenses%20and%20provides%20first%20aid%20kits.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVivek%20emphasises%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20way%2C%20we%20address%20any%20doubts%20community%20members%20may%20have%20about%20the%20program%2C%20ensuring%20that%20their%20questions%20are%20answered%20satisfactorily.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMatthew%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20when%20I%20played%20rugby%20with%20young%20people%2C%20I%20believed%20that%20helping%20them%20secure%20jobs%20would%20lead%20to%20economic%20stability.%20However%2C%20we%20realised%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20ready%20for%20a%20structured%20work%20environment.%20This%20setback%20inspired%20our%20%E2%80%9CChildhood%20to%20Livelihood%E2%80%9D%20programme.%20We%20understood%20that%20getting%20them%20jobs%20was%20only%20half%20the%20battle%3B%20keeping%20them%20employed%20required%20equipping%20them%20with%20the%20right%20skills%20and%20guidance%20to%20enter%20the%20workforce.%20It%E2%80%99s%20where%20they%20grasp%20the%20value%20of%20work%2C%20learn%20skills%20beyond%20their%20chosen%20profession%2C%20and%20evolve%20into%20role%20models%2C%20actively%20breaking%20the%20cycle%20of%20poverty%20for%20their%20families%20and%20the%20entire%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F3_11zon-1698735055.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20big%20part%20of%20Magic%20Bus%20India%20Foundation's%20work%20is%20to%20provide%20vocational%20skills'%20training%20to%20Indian%20kids%20to%20ensure%20a%20secure%20future.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F3_11zon-1698735055.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F3_11zon-1698735055-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F3_11zon-1698735055-500x500.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F3_11zon-1698735055-150x150.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F3_11zon-1698735055-768x768.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F3_11zon-1698735055-96x96.jpeg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333300%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20big%20part%20of%20Magic%20Bus%20India%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20work%20is%20to%20provide%20vocational%20skills%20training%20to%20Indian%20kids%20to%20ensure%20a%20secure%20future.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Showed%20me%20the%20right%20path%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EVivek%20points%20to%20the%20example%20of%20Prachi%2C%20a%20young%20girl%20who%20had%20previously%20never%20left%20her%20village.%20Last%20year%20she%20travelled%20to%20a%20national%20athletic%20competition%20in%20Ranchi%2C%20Bihar.%20%E2%80%9CHer%20parents%20were%20in%20complete%20shock%20that%20a%20girl%20who%20never%20left%20the%20home%20before%20has%20performed%20in%20this%20kind%20of%20event%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98If%20you%20had%20not%20tried%20with%20our%20child%2C%20she%20would%20never%20have%20reached%20this%20level.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20girl%20who%20has%20benefitted%20from%20Magic%20Bus%E2%80%99%20interventions%20is%2017-year-old%20Bittu%20Kumari.%20She%20joined%20the%20programme%20in%202017%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330978%2Fkamlesh-atwal-started-nanakmatta-public-school-uttarakhand-holistic-education-for-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20Class%208%20student%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20says%20she%20learned%20life%20skills%20through%20volleyball%20and%20kabaddi%20(volleyball%20has%20since%20been%20replaced%20with%20cricket).%20According%20to%20her%2C%20Magic%20Bus%20helped%20her%20make%20the%20optimum%20use%20of%20her%20talent%20as%20a%20kabaddi%20player.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20I%20am%20a%20state-level%20kabaddi%20player%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20play%20at%20the%20national%20level%20also%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20had%20not%20found%20Magic%20Bus%2C%20I%20would%20not%20have%20made%20it%20this%20far.%20They%20showed%20me%20the%20right%20path.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20process%2C%20she%20has%20gone%20from%20being%20scared%20to%20speak%20to%20people%20to%20having%20the%20confidence%20to%20speak%20to%20anyone.%20%E2%80%9CMagic%20Bus%20taught%20me%20communication%20skills%2C%20gave%20me%20confidence%2C%20taught%20me%20what%20is%20right%20and%20what%20is%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20year%20Magic%20Bus%20appointed%20Bittu%20as