and%20upliftment%20of%20girls%20and%20women%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20events%20of%20the%20Toofaan%20Games%20that%20the%20girls%20participate%20in%20are%20the%2050m%20sprint%2C%20shuttle%20run%2C%20standing%20long%20jump%2C%20and%20endurance%20run.%20These%20four%20events%20were%20selected%20because%20they%20are%20simple%2C%20easy%20to%20conduct%20and%20give%20the%20girls%20an%20opportunity%20to%20demonstrate%20their%20speed%2C%20agility%2C%20lower%20body%20strength%20and%20stamina.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAbout%20130%20girls%20make%20it%20to%20the%20final%20stage%20of%20the%20Toofaan%20Games%20each%20year%20and%20for%20many%20of%20them%2C%20the%20games%20are%20the%20first%20time%20they%20set%20foot%20outside%20their%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20significant%20point%20to%20emphasise%20here%20is%20that%20the%20initiative%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F101981%2Fuplabdhi-misha-chandola-teach-girls-project-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eled%20by%20women%20entirely%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20right%20from%20coaching%20to%20the%20results.%20The%20existing%20infrastructure%20at%20Naandi%20%E2%80%94%20under%20the%20Nanhi%20Kali%20programme%20%E2%80%94%20has%20propelled%20the%20movement%20in%20a%20short%20span%20of%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98Nanhi%20Kali%20after-school%20tuition%20centres%E2%80%99%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261243%2Fmalnutrition-orphanage-girl-child-hyderabad-women-donation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanaged%20by%20a%20young%20woman%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20same%20community%20as%20the%20girls.%20When%20sports%20were%20introduced%2C%20these%20tutors%20were%20to%20deliver%20the%20weekly%20sports%20drills%20and%20practices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20first%20year%20it%20was%20optional%20for%20tutors%20to%20become%20%E2%80%98sports%20allies%E2%80%99.%20About%20half%20of%20them%20said%20that%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20do%20it%20because%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20it%20was.%20By%20the%20second%20year%2C%20everyone%20wanted%20to%20do%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rohini%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20tutors%20initially%20went%20in%20not%20knowing%20what%20to%20expect%2C%20but%20once%20they%20experienced%20it%2C%20everyone%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20event%2C%20back%20in%202020%2C%20vindicated%20their%20belief%20about%20the%20benefits%20of%20sports%20and%20physical%20activity%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20result%20of%20the%20organisation%20inculcating%20sports%20into%20their%20work%20and%20regular%20programming.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20videos%20and%20photos%20of%20the%20girls%20doing%20these%20sports%20drills%20were%20sent%20back%20and%20forth%20over%20WhatsApp%20to%20the%20sports%20allies.%20To%20streamline%20this%20process%20further%2C%20Naandi%20decided%20to%20create%20its%20own%20app%20called%20SportStar%20to%20create%20a%20database.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20once%20a%20week%2C%20a%20video%20of%20a%20sports%20drill%20is%20sent%20out%20to%20roughly%206%2C000%20sports%20allies.%20This%20allows%20for%20feedback%20and%20collaboration%20among%20all%20of%20them%20as%20everyone%20shares%20their%20training%20videos%2C%20which%20ensures%20that%20the%20app%20has%20more%20content%20for%20their%20perusal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20girls%20cannot%20relate%20to%20YouTube%20videos%20of%20foreigners%20doing%20these%20drills.%20With%20this%20exchange%20of%20videos%2C%20we%20have%20ended%20up%20creating%20more%20resources%20for%20our%20girls%20to%20imbibe%20information%20from.%20The%20app%20is%20not%20open%20to%20the%20public%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rohini.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20girl%20is%20doing%20some%20exercise%20well%2C%20then%20we%20use%20that%20video%20during%20our%20drills%20across%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20