age.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETheir%20new%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20year%20after%20its%20inception%2C%20the%20first%2012%20girls%20were%20transferred%20from%20the%20government%20orphanage%20by%20the%20order%20of%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Child%20Welfare%20Committee.%20At%20this%20new%20home%2C%20the%20girls%20shared%20living%20spaces%2C%20recreational%20activities%2C%20and%20got%20education.%20To%20encourage%20the%20girls%20to%20speak%20in%20their%20mother%20tongue%2C%20Dr%20Michelle%20enrolled%20them%20in%20a%20Bengali%20medium%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20start%20introducing%20English%20learning%20until%20Class%205.%20It%20was%20difficult%20to%20find%20teachers%20who%20taught%20them%20seriously.%20After%20several%20years%2C%20and%20the%20girls%20taking%20insults%20from%20the%20teachers%2C%20we%20started%20our%20own%20school%20and%20relied%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326013%2Fbengaluru-friends-run-gubacchi-non-profit-to-educate-migrant-worker-children-for-free%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Institute%20for%20Open%20Schooling%20%3C%2Fa%3E(NIOS)%20for%20the%20board%20exams%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20established%20a%20smart%20centre%20for%20children%20which%20is%20a%20free%20and%20inclusive%20play%20school%20for%20underprivileged%20children%20aged%20between%202%20and%204%20years%20in%20the%20community.%20The%20school%20includes%20play-based%20and%20activity-based%20learning%2C%20focuses%20on%20the%20development%20of%20social%20skills%20in%20preparation%20for%20formal%20schooling%2C%20and%20a%20nutritious%20snack%2C%20says%20Dr%20Michelle.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20girls%20live%20in%20a%20warm%20and%20loving%20home%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20a%20sterile%20environment%20that%20often%20embodies%20a%20government%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20Shishur%20