sed%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do%20it.%20India%20is%20now%20my%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Dr%20Michelle%20Harrison.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698419195000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333185%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20receiving%20death%20threats%2C%20Israeli-origin%20Dr%20Michelle%20Harrison%20dedicated%20her%20life%20to%20providing%20safe%20space%20and%20a%20future%20to%20orphaned%20girls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Homage%20to%20Heritage%3A%20Why%20I%20Spent%2025%20Years%20Painting%20India%E2%80%99s%20Iconic%20Steam%20Trains%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUntil%201995%2C%20the%20familiar%20chug-chug-chug%20of%20steam%20locomotives%20hustling%20along%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F295743%2Funsung-hero-indian-railways-driver-manasser-johannes-saved-passengers-on-burning-train%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20railway%20lines%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20a%20regular%20sound%20to%20many.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20aficionados%20of%20steam%20locomotives%20can%20still%20hop%20onto%20the%20Darjeeling%20Himalayan%20Railway%20(DHR)%20and%20Nilgiri%20Mountain%20Railway%20(NMR)%20to%20experience%20the%20thrill%20of%20this%20heritage%20form%20of%20transport%2C%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Indian%20railway%20scene%20has%20undergone%20a%20radical%20transformation.%20A%20fleet%20of%20diesel%20engines%20has%20replaced%20the%20steam%20ones%20through%20the%20years%2C%20marking%20an%20end%20to%20an%20era.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20even%20after%20the%20steam%20engines%20were%20phased%20out%2C%20Kishore%20Pratim%20Biswas%2C%20a%20Kolkata-born%20artist%2C%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20ready%20to%20part%20with%20these%20memories.%20Born%20in%201971%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20he%E2%80%99d%20spent%20his%20years%20growing%20up%20watching%20the%20steam%20locomotives.%20Rides%20on%20the%20engine%20would%20often%20be%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F303089%2Faditya-raj-artist-sketches-heritage-restaurants-iconic-spots-in-mumbai-delhi-kyani-nirulas-instagram%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccompanied%20by%20tales%3C%2Fa%3E%20narrated%20by%20his%20uncle%20who%20was%20a%20locomotive%20driver.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSometimes%20I%20rode%20in%20the%20engine%20with%20the%20motorman%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20remarkable%20experience.%20I%20got%20to%20witness%20how%20they%20work%20in%20close%20quarters.%20The%20engine%20used%20to%20be%20very%20hot%20and%20they%20had%20to%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20in%20it%20and%20yet%20they%20kept%20a%20smiling%20face%20and%20never%20complained.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKishore%20graduated%20in%20Fine%20Arts%20from%20the%20Government%20College%20of%20Art%20%26amp%3B%20Craft%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20in%201996%2C%20but%20struggled%20with%20the%20dearth%20of%20opportunities%20in%20the%20city.%C2%A0%20In%202009%2C%20Kishore%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20Mumbai%2C%20which%20opened%20the%20doors%20to%20new%20opportunities.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325308%2Frare-wildlife-conservation-photos-from-across-the-world-nature-infocus-kalyan-varma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtemporary%20artist%3C%2Fa%3E%20cultivates%20a%20spirit%20of%20nostalgia%20through%20every%20project%20he%20undertakes%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98Indian%20Steam%20Locomotives%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20series%20he%20spent%2025%20years%20working%20on%2C%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20his%20craft.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20series%2C%20he%20creates%20an%20unmatched%20visual%20experience%20of%20the%20locos%2C%20the%20journey%20and%20the%20experience%20that%20was%20enjoyed%20by%20people%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9970s.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHistory%20on%20wheels%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EWatching%20the%20white%20steam%20of%20the%20locos%20billowing%20against%20the%20black%20engine%20are%20some%20of%20Kishore%E2%80%99s%20fondest%20childhood%20memories.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20dramatic%20visual%20experience%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%2C%20adding%20that%20when%20he%20had%20to%20take%20up%20his%20first%20art%20project%2C%20he%20wanted%20it%20to%20be%20an%20ode%20to%20this%20memory.%20Their%20%E2%80%9Cunusual%20character%E2%80%9D%20was%20something%20he%20wanted%20to%20highlight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKishore%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F251201%2Findian-railways-baba-bhalku-rail-museum-kalka-shimla-railway-unesco-heritage-british-india-history-san37%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecolours%20of%20the%20engine%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20mostly%20black%20and%20grey%2C%20while%20the%20body%20looked%20too%20muddy%2C%20dusty%20and%20unclean.%20But%20this%20gave%20its%20surface%20a%20unique%20look%20and%20lent%20the%20locomotives%20a%20distinct%20character.%20I%20have%20never%20found%20anything%20in%20the%20world%20as%20interesting%20as%20these%20trains.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20the%2042-year-old%20artist%20looks%20back%20on%20the%20last%2015%20years%20and%20the%20art%20series%20he%20has%20taken%20up%2C%20he%20says%20the%20journey%20has%20strengthened%20his%20unconventional%20thought%20process.%20It%20has%20also%20orchestrated%20his%20painting%20style%2C%20which%20has%20transitioned%20from%20watercolours%20to%20acrylics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20how%20he%20curated%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F229283%2Findian-railways-rare-pictures-history-first-train-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20locomotive%20series%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Kishore%20says%20its%20inception%20was%20during%20his%20time%20in%20Kolkata.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20visit%20the%20railway%20workshops%20in%20the%20city%20every%20morning%20to%20sketch%20the%20locomotives.%20I%20would%20spend%20almost%20five%20to%20six%20hours%20every%20day%20doing%20this.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBreathing%20life%20into%20these%20sketches%20through%20watercolour%2C%20oil%2C%20pen%20and%20ink%20was%20a%20fulfilling%20process%20for%20Kishore.%20But%20the%20excitement%20came%20to%20an%20end%20one%20day%20in%201993%20when%20Kishore%20watched%20the%20steam%20locos%20being%20dismantled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20being%20scrapped%20as%20they%20were%20no%20longer%20being%20operational.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20shocking%20experience%20for%20me%20and%20I%20was%20left%20in%20tears%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20While%20Kishore%20returned%20to%20Mumbai%20to%20complete%20the%20series%20%E2%80%94%20this%20time%20from%20the%20memory%20of%20what%20he%20had%20seen%20%E2%80%94%20he%20decided%20to%20turn%20it%20into%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F279321%2Fart-beautify-railway-station-project-nilesh-nagra-indore-stunning-pictures%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20than%20just%20a%20painting%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20engines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20captured%20the%20movement%20of%20people%20including%20the%20fireman%2C%20signalman%2C%20technical%20man%2C%20motorman%20and%20others%20working%20in%20the%20locomotive%20workshops.%20My%20paintings%20always%20have%20a%20deep%20expression%20of%20the%20characters%2C%20with%20dark%2C%20bearded%20faces%20sporting%20a%20red%20%3Cem%3Epagdi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(turban)%20which%20looks%20very%20unusual%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C